# ── Rust build artifacts ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
target/
**/*.rs.bk
**/.cargo/

# ── Lean build artifacts ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
lean/.lake/
lean/**.olean
lean/**.ilean
lean/**.trace

# ── Git ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.git/
.gitignore
.githooks/

# ── CI / editor ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.github/
.vscode/
.idea/

# ── Docs / transcripts (not needed in image) ─────────────────────────────
docs/
transcripts/
roadmap-v2.md
*.md

# ── Dev / test artifacts ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
*.tmp
*.swp
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ── Secrets / environment ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
secrets/

# ── Keep bundled assets needed in the image (override the broad ignores above) ──
# The runtime image bundles the system prompt; without these negations the
# `*.md` rule above could strip prompts/lean-prover.md from the build context.
!prompts/
!prompts/**
